---
import { HeadinPrincipal } from "../ui/heading-principal";
import WordRotate from "../ui/word_rotate";
import GraphicFigureLogo from "../widgets/graphic-figure-logo.astro";
---

<section id="hero">
  <div
    class="container relative flex h-auto w-full flex-col items-start pb-8 pt-20 lg:-mt-10 lg:min-h-[calc(100vh-10rem)] lg:justify-center lg:pb-0 lg:pt-0"
  >
    <section class="">
      <HeadinPrincipal
        client:load
        words="Forjar el camino en el detalle y los valores"
        className="h1 mb-5 text-white font-normal max-md:max-w-[30rem] md:max-w-[640px] lg:mb-7 xl:max-w-[740px]"
      />
      <p
        class="md:mb-5 animate-fade-in-up w-[17rem] sm:w-[25rem] text-[20px] font-thin text-gray-200 animate-delay-[1200ms] animate-duration-500 md:w-[34rem] md:text-[26px] md:leading-9 lg:text-[28px]"
      >
        Transformamos tu visión empresarial en una realidad digital con <WordRotate
          client:load
          words={[
            "Diseño y Estrategia",
            "Desarrollo Web",
            "Gestión Multimedia",
            "Producción de Contenido",
          ]}
        />
      </p>
      <!-- <p class="text-gray-200 lg:w-[34rem] text-base lg:text-lg mb-14 animate-duration-500 animate-delay-[1200ms] animate-fade-in-up -mt-20">
        ¿Preparado para iniciar?   ¡Forjemos una relación de trabajo íntegra y fructífera. Para llevar tu empresa al mundo virtual con estilo y originalidad!
      </p> -->

      <div
        class="flex animate-fade-in-up items-center gap-x-4 text-sm animate-delay-[1800ms] animate-duration-500 lg:text-base"
      >
        <!-- <a href="#contact" class="text-sm lg:text-base inline-block tracking-widesttext-black font-inter px-4 lg:px-6 rounded-full py-2 font-bold bg-gradient-to-r bg-white btn-learn-more hover:bg-transparent border-2 border-transparent hover:border-white transition-all hover:text-white hover:scale-[1.03]">CONTACTANOS</a> -->

        <a
          href="#about-us"
          class="btn-learn-more inline-block rounded-full border-2 border-white px-4 py-2 font-inter text-sm font-bold tracking-widest text-white transition-all hover:scale-[1.03] hover:bg-white hover:text-black lg:px-6 lg:text-base"
          >CONOCÉ MÁS</a
        >
      </div>
    </section>
  </div>
</section>

<GraphicFigureLogo />

<div class="glow pointer-events-none"></div>

<style>
  .glow-2::before,
  .glow::after,
  . {
    background: var(--primary-glow);
    width: 240px;
    height: 180px;
    z-index: -1;
  }

  .glow::before {
    z-index: -1;
  }

  .glow::before,
  .glow::after {
    content: "";
    top: 12%;
    left: -32%;
    position: absolute;
    opacity: 10;
    filter: blur(35px);
    transform: translateZ(0);
  }

  .glow-2::before,
  .glow-2::after {
    content: "";
    bottom: 34%;
    right: -2%;
    opacity: 0.4;
    position: absolute;
    filter: blur(70px);
    transform: translateZ(0);
  }

  @media (min-width: 1024px) {
    .glow::before,
    .glow::after {
      left: -6%;
    }
  }
</style>
